Package: urogynScorer
Title: Calculate Scores for Urogynecology Questionnaires
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tyler", "Muffly", , "tyler.muffly@dhha.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9374-9525"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for scoring, validating, and analyzing
    patient-reported outcome measures (PROMs) used in urogynecology and pelvic
    floor medicine. The package implements standardized scoring algorithms with
    robust validation for commonly used questionnaires including PFDI-20, 
    PGI-I, and Sandvik Severity Index.
